mmetry. The topological phase is affirmed by edge\nstate calculation, obeying the bulk-boundary correspondence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2017 10:23:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-25"}
