 given by the SU(6) symmetry,\nclose to values generally used in the literature. However, the $\\Lambda$\npotential in $\\Lambda$ matter varies between -16 and -8 MeV taking for vector\nmesons couplings the SU(6) values, at variance with generally employed values\nbetween $-1$ and $-5$ MeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2017 13:14:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-21"}
